-- Bahrain's Investcorp H1 net profit surges 53 pct 
-- By Mirna Sleiman
-- Sun Feb 02, 2014 12:13AM EST
-- None



DUBAI, Feb 2 (Reuters) - Bahrain-based alternative investment manager Investcorp <INVB.BH> said on Sunday that profit for the first half of its fiscal year rose 53 percent, mainly because of strong performances at its core businesses.

